% parrot0 coding knowledge — gen149 ground layer.
% C/Python language facts, error patterns, and stdlib functions.
% ONE clause per line (the kb_load parser reads one line at a time).
% Loaded at boot; queryable by mod_code for inline code debugging.
% Format: see DESIGN.md (D1-D3).

% --- Language identification features ------------------------------
language(c).
language(python).

% C keywords (one per line for reliable parsing)
